{"tid":2376870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丹麥戰線｜丹麥跨黨派企硬 香港黑警計劃起訴及引渡兩丹麥議員 政壇齊撐 給予無限支持","createTime":"2021-01-23T06:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T07:09:24.000Z","uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4a58a31e1be8998331534a820436d0ff707680","tid":2376870,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2457763871041598\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fposts%2F2457763871041598&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5JMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=7661e86e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2457763871041598</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警早前計劃起訴及引渡兩名協助許智峯流亡的丹麥議員，事件引起當地國會對華大團結，當中執政社會民主黨議員Annette Lind、反對黨自由黨Michael Aastrup Jensen 、「第三大黨」社會自由黨兼外交政策委員會主席Martin Lidegaard剛發表聯合聲明，聲援受中共打壓的議會同事。<br />\n聲明表示，丹麥憲法保障國會議員可以無懼報復下自由地履行職務，雖則他們平時與兩名受中共針對的國會同事Katarina Ammitzb&oslash;ll 及 Uffe Elb&aelig;k或有政見不同，但強調今次對他們給予無限支持，反對任何將議員職位及自由權利刑事化的行徑。<br />\n他們呼籲更多議員加入聯署，令更多黨派議員認清中共及《國安法》的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n丹麥豬、雞高汁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413ede256494487183508a294c19c27dd066c3b8","tid":2376870,"uid":43278,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:38:47.000Z","msg":"政見不同嘅黨派呢個時候唔係掩住嘴笑鳩人<br />\n而係大團結聯署公開撐<br />\n型到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c125490f22148f5b7340adc160b3c00d8d57bc","tid":2376870,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"小心中共特務o係丹麥地頭搞搞震就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n引度唔到人都要隊冧人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3cfa60008fc0ee9bbdfa0867d3c0ad8faa936d","tid":2376870,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"而家各國想用支那做共同敵人去團結內部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d21c07d95980566e31eabe1d4046f76d504695","tid":2376870,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"邊個同佢引渡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090fc91fd0f58d67d6be8e7d136145e7f7a4f32f","tid":2376870,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38d21c07d95980566e31eabe1d4046f76d504695","tid":2376870,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"邊個同佢引渡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"洗頭艇: 我"},{"pid":"7af523e95e7afea03b965d8acdc504982c1a4aa7","tid":2376870,"uid":67298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38d21c07d95980566e31eabe1d4046f76d504695","tid":2376870,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:02:31.000Z","msg":"邊個同佢引渡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:09:24.000Z","msg":"派D散仔去捉人偷渡返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}